  "texts": [
    "A purposive sampling method was employed for the selection of participants.",
    "The sampling strategy aimed to ensure that the participants possess a specialized postgraduate degree in the respective specialty of dentistry as part of inclusion criteria.",
    "Considering the recommendations, the number of experts for content validation should be at least six and does not exceed ten [13].",
    "Therefore, a total of 36 participants (9 belonging to each four specialties of dentistry i.e., Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery, Operative Dentistry & Endodontics, Periodontics and Prosthodontics) formed the study sample.",
    "To eliminate bias in grading, the experts were blinded to the responses generated via both models."
  ],
